{"tid":103424,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"突登開個AC，就係想同你哋講呢件事。","createTime":"2017-02-01T10:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T04:26:46.000Z","uid":81292,"like":9,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32152e1e7a13c22551c0c907bfbaa69a50561c7d","tid":103424,"uid":81292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:29:32.000Z","msg":"我同一個女仔經歷過好多事，<br />\n感情真係唔錯，甚至佢會同我講我係佢最重視嘅人。<br />\n因為好珍惜佢所以一直都唔同佢講我歡喜佢。<br />\n一直都只不過用個心嚟對佢好。<br />\n我未試過咁努力地對一個女仔好，想佢開心。<br />\n但係原來咁樣對自己真係好辛苦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一次同朋友傾計忍唔住講咗出嚟，但係條粉皮背住我同翻個女仔講，真正嘅惡夢正式開始。"},{"pid":"60a52927971da994f6c75a6aa7745ce5cb5550c2","tid":103424,"uid":78009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:35:17.000Z","msg":"熱心撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90235f6b4f4ec7fc5878e8249c5968f2d4e61c3a","tid":103424,"uid":10620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:37:02.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"ef0997a4505cfdebd9bc7cbb568fcd2ea0f9bddb","tid":103424,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:37:10.000Z","msg":"繼續"},{"pid":"aafd83bb6e0849a1d34c61bc67f2337052a60529","tid":103424,"uid":8990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:38:25.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"4d9ce865f62f1d7916e6c1a00059311a3a52db0a","tid":103424,"uid":20460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:41:44.000Z","msg":"真名上lihkg?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7225b08bce921417cfbf58570d0e855e44dc4e24","tid":103424,"uid":81323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:45:20.000Z","msg":"不說一句的愛有多好<br />\n他不是男朋友卻比男朋友更親更重要"},{"pid":"34a74d57c27844de542fa29ced6eace168229265","tid":103424,"uid":81292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:45:49.000Z","msg":"有一晚，個女仔同我講話佢鍾意咗個男仔。嗰刻我好唔開心，並唔係因為佢鍾意咗個男仔，而係因為個男嘅曾經同我講過，佢有幾唔鍾意呢個女仔。<br />\n我係擔心佢，但真係唔想佢唔開心，我只好係咁氹佢，「會幸福㗎」「要加油呀」，嗰晚喺手機扮到好積極，但其實我頹到瞓唔著，自己chur曬成包煙⋯⋯"},{"pid":"a5b9d8bf413794a28a6e6c99c9ce0e88805ef0d3","tid":103424,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:52:58.000Z","msg":"留低條腳毛先"},{"pid":"c368c219a357868a9f1a90e61aa264e7ca8083ab","tid":103424,"uid":81292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:44:06.000Z","msg":"自問預感真係幾準，特別係人同人之間嘅關係。<br />\n唔知點解，喺佢同我講完佢鍾意咗個男仔之後一日，我突然有一個念頭，會唔會係佢突登呃我，唔想我繼續鍾意佢呢？<br />\n越諗成件事越可疑。<br />\n終於有一次成班人食飯，我趁佢去厠所，我拎咗佢電話嚟睇。（千祈唔好學我，到而家都覺得自己好撚仆街）<br />\n我估撚中曬⋯⋯<br />\n我嗰吓真係寧願佢真係鍾意咗個男仔，咁樣都起碼叫冇呃我。<br />\n我屈埋咗自己幾日，終於忍唔住，想同佢講清楚。"},{"pid":"6814ce154878147fceaa0cba81fbb296c85a1e8d","tid":103424,"uid":10620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:51:28.000Z","msg":"條女咁撚樣就絕交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲同佢傾計簡直折磨"},{"pid":"b720749f5be947e5a57f23b1ab54ff835f82bd55","tid":103424,"uid":71847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:52:35.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b4239d24941024bf53650aa6e59d480d6f1e8064","tid":103424,"uid":42815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:59:39.000Z","msg":"感情真係一科好難學的東西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21dede4872bfb96c90636b0325f2202f2bc0465","tid":103424,"uid":81292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:52:40.000Z","msg":"嗰日，我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「你同佢而家點呀？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「冇呀其實都冇乜聯絡，冇進展。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「其實你係咪真係鍾意佢㗎？」<br />\n佢顯得有啲遲疑，比咗個模稜兩可嘅答案我。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「其實我都唔知呀，可能係好感啩。」<br />\n呢一刻，我哋行到公園門口，入去坐低咗。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「其實你都知冇嘢瞞到我㗎。」<br />\n佢呢刻靜咗。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「點解突登要揾啲咁嘅嘢呃我？」<br />\n佢開始喊，越喊越犀利，就好似佢第一次比朋友拋棄，喺我面前喊，嗰次我好痛心佢，攬住佢安慰佢。<br />\n但係今次我真係唔知點氹佢，我只係拍住佢膊頭。<br />\n大約五分鐘之後，佢終於開聲⋯⋯"},{"pid":"55a7bac591cc51bfb3a54ea6294d87dc06ec2267","tid":103424,"uid":79093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28e565943979fbae571ca6e6cb9c3006001b360","tid":103424,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T15:02:28.000Z","msg":"想睇落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"799251234393164a866699c211a7de24210f7e6a","tid":103424,"uid":34692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"如果你係用真名我可能識你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921df79d7e142d4930644886ae373826416b911f","tid":103424,"uid":81292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:20:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你係用真名我可能識你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係真名，<br />\nBetween 大專生應該十個有五至六個都識何善衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25c61f98d04e9fd194ebacd9965f66b341a72b0","tid":103424,"uid":16797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:22:35.000Z","msg":"加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8784036349ff6722512f083b67498e52eb022346","tid":103424,"uid":66152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:23:16.000Z","msg":"手機響鈴來留名"},{"pid":"763b41e6d69c05c2a0ab6e9ecd9fc9c15bce343f","tid":103424,"uid":50331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:40:58.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"2370fb7e27bdd3d6a4008b195af13c20e182f36b","tid":103424,"uid":17849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:44:54.000Z","msg":"繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8571a802632d85d694c209493fa40f4fea3f84","tid":103424,"uid":81292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"佢終於肯開口。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「係因為我知道咗呀。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「知道咗啲咩？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「XX同我講咗。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「所以呢？你真係咁憎我？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「唔係呀，我知道你好辛苦呀，我唔想繼續咁落去，我覺得咁對你好唔公平呀。」<br />\n之後我哋又靜咗陣，嗰刻我乜都唔想講，但其實又好多嘢想講。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「如果冇人話你知，你又真係唔知我對你係點咩？」<br />\n佢又靜咗陣。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「就係因為有人同我講，我先唔可以咁繼續落去呀！」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「你而家呃咗我咁又點啫？你知唔知你同我講完之後，我最大嘅感受係咩呀？唔係SAD尻呀，係我好撚擔心你呀！」<br />\n之後我將所有事話曬比佢知。<br />\n佢繼續喊，冇停過。<br />\n之後我講咗一句我自己講完都覺得好心酸嘅說話。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「其實我都知冇可能㗎，不過我一直都願意做好好朋友呢個角色，我又冇試過去越過呢條界，點解你一定要破壞佢啫？」<br />\n嗰晚嘅思緒好亂，圓場係點打我已經唔記得。但我剩係記得等佢喊完，之後就去食飯，最後送佢返屋企，就完啦。"},{"pid":"5d9ec9204a3355960e9b559293ebd2b945bc09d6","tid":103424,"uid":79275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:51:47.000Z","msg":"何苦呢Ching<br />\n呢啲好好朋友位真係咁好坐？"},{"pid":"993874234d0b1ba4c073f0c423bb35905aa96e4d","tid":103424,"uid":27099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:55:54.000Z","msg":"💂🏿"},{"pid":"1b1ef30f426254682d